'''Arno Marais''' (yavutse 19 Mata 1984), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri  [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] . Azwi cyane kubera uruhare rwe muri ''seri'' zizwi cyane Stroomop, ''Die Boekklub'' na ''Reconnect'' .

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 19 Mata 1984 i Bloemfontein muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]. Nyina ni Corrie Viviers.

== Umwuga ==
Mu 2009, yakinnye nk'inzobere mu by'ikoranabuhanga 'Benjamin le Roux' muri opera izwi cyane ''Isidingo'' aho igice cye cyanyuze ku ya 20 Ugushyingo. <ref>https://www.tvsa.co.za/actors/viewactor.aspx?actorid=16514</ref> Muri 2016, yagaragaye muri serivise yikinamico ya kykNET ''Die Boekklub'' akina nka 'Herman Mouton'. Mu mpera za 2016, yagize ikiruhuko cyimyaka ibiri kuva ''Isidingo'' . Muri kiriya gihe, yinjiye mu bakinnyi ba televiziyo ya ''Sokhulu & Partners'' maze akina nka 'Adv. Nick Edwards '. Hanyuma yagaragaye kuri serial ''7de Laan'' muburyo bugaruka. Hanyuma muri 2017, asubira muri ''Isidingo'' . <ref>https://www.iol.co.za/entertainment/arno-marais-is-back-on-isidingo-9432520</ref>

== Impanuka ==
Ku ya 28 Nyakanga 2010, yagize impanuka y'imodoka yahitanye Kobus Venter, umwangavu. Marais yarakomeretse cyane aguma muri koma ibyumweru bine mu bitaro by’amasomo bya Steve Biko i Pretoria. <ref>https://www.news24.com/You/Archive/isidingos-arno-moms-coma-vigal-20170728</ref> Nk’uko amakuru aturuka mu bitaro abitangaza, ngo yabyimbye mu bwonko mu gihe cya koma ndetse no kuva amaraso imbere. Yasize ibihaha yarajanjaguwe, bityo akoresha ubuhumekero. <ref>https://www.pressreader.com/south-africa/the-citizen-kzn/20100728/282260956747682</ref> Yamaze ibyumweru bitandatu mu bitaro. <ref>https://www.news24.com/You/Archive/isidingos-arno-marais-charged-after-crash-20170728</ref> Mu mwaka wa 2012, yitabye urukiko bwa mbere muri Pretoria ku bijyanye n'impanuka. <ref>https://www.iol.co.za/news/isidingo-star-in-court-after-fatal-accident-1378612</ref>

== Impaka ==
Muri 2018, yashyizeho Tweets nyinshi yibasira Abayisilamu kandi yatanze ibitekerezo bimwe bikemangwa kuri Islam . <ref>https://www.thesouthafrican.com/news/isidingo-star-arno-marais-islam-tweets/</ref>

